<HEADLINE> Shanghai Bank Offers Insurance for Credit Card Holders </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, May 17 (Xinhua) -- The Shanghai branch of the Bank of
Communications has developed an insurance service for its credit
card holders at a local university.
</P>
<P>
Apart from the normal advantages the bank card provides for
shopping, etc., card holders at Tongji University are also
automatically insured against accidents, losing the card and
damage to their property, according to bank officials.
</P>
<P>
The new function is aimed at providing comprehensive financial
services for teachers and students at local universities, the
officials explained.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, the bank has decided to donate half of the revenue
from the credit card to Tongji University. 
</P>
</TEXT>
