the new Nordic-Tanzanian partnership.
</P>
<P>
Speaking at a state banquet he hosted for the visiting Finnish
President Marti Ahtisaari on Friday, Mkapa said he was eager for
a gradual change of co-operation to one sustained by investments
and trade.
</P>
<P>
