The Thai court issued a warrant for his arrest after the bail
jumper failed to appear before the court to face charges in March.
</P>
<P>
He was captured within the Myanmar territory.
</P>
<P>
The Myanmar authorities said the handing over of the absconder
was aimed at promoting good relations between Myanmar and Thailand
and at effective fight against narcotic drugs in the region.
